# Documentation Maintenance Rule

- Whenever a critical functionality change is made, update both:
  - `README.md`
  - `src/genesis/instruments/DRIVER_AUTHORING_GUIDE.md`
- Include user-facing behavior changes, operational workflow updates, and any driver-impacting runtime/safety changes.
- Before finishing work, verify these two documents are still accurate for the new behavior.
- When providing a context handoff/summary for the next agent, explicitly include:
  - whether these two docs were updated,
  - what sections changed,
  - and any pending documentation follow-ups.
